ory_Training_Group_UK_1000x.png?v=1686151147 768w, https://cdn.shopify.com/s/files/1/0937/2788/files/Oliver_McGowan_The_Journey_to_Mandatory_Training_for_Learning_Disability_and_Autism_-_Oliver_McGowan_Mandatory_Training_-_Mandatory_Training_Group_UK_500x.png?v=1686151147 320w" width="1374" height="458" alt="Oliver McGowan: The Journey to Mandatory Training for Learning Disability and Autism - Oliver McGowan Mandatory Training - Mandatory Training Group UK -" title="Oliver McGowan: The Journey to Mandatory Training for Learning Disability and Autism - Oliver McGowan Mandatory Training - Mandatory Training Group UK -" data-pf-type="Image3" class="sc-igXgud kyVXGU pf-15_"/></div></div></div></div></div><div data-section-id="pf-e0ad" data-category="Generic Content" data-name="Matcha" data-pf-type="Section" class="sc-fTxOGA fdxuCs pf-16_"><div style="--cw:1170px" class="sc-hRMWxn klCafx"><div class="sc-ikJyIC iIcPdk pf-17_ pf-r pf-r-eh" style="--s-xs:0px;--s-sm:15px" data-pf-type="Row"><div class="pf-c" style="--c-xs:12;--c-md:12;--c-lg:12"><div data-pf-type="Column" class="sc-lhMiDA kOJwSu pf-18_"><p class="sc-gfqkcP gZrsGP pf-19_" data-pf-type="Paragraph"><span data-pf-type="Text" class="sc-jdhwqr jnAcXR pf-21_">In significant health and social care sector development, the long-awaited Oliver McGowan Mandatory Training in Learning Disability and Autism was officially launched in England on November 4, 2022. Dedicated advocates, including Oliver's parents, Tom and Paula McGowan, have worked tirelessly for years to achieve this momentous occasion. Ultimately, their efforts resulted in a directive requiring mandatory learning disability and autism training for all health and social care workers.
