<br>
</span></p><h2 data-pf-type="Heading" class="sc-bBHHxi aumKe pf-22_ _Y6RW61"><span data-pf-type="Text" class="sc-jdhwqr jnAcXR pf-24_">Parliamentary discussions: A call for better understanding

</span></h2><img src="https://cdn.shopify.com/s/files/1/0937/2788/files/Parliamentary_discussions_A_call_for_better_understanding_-_Oliver_McGowan_Mandatory_Training_-_Mandatory_Training_Group_UK.png?v=1686151424" srcSet="https://cdn.shopify.com/s/files/1/0937/2788/files/Parliamentary_discussions_A_call_for_better_understanding_-_Oliver_McGowan_Mandatory_Training_-_Mandatory_Training_Group_UK.png?v=1686151424 1536w, https://cdn.shopify.com/s/files/1/0937/2788/files/Parliamentary_discussions_A_call_for_better_understanding_-_Oliver_McGowan_Mandatory_Training_-_Mandatory_Training_Group_UK_500x.png?v=1686151424 320w" width="1702" height="1072" alt="Parliamentary discussions: A call for better understanding - Oliver McGowan Mandatory Training - Mandatory Training Group UK -" title="Parliamentary discussions: A call for better understanding - Oliver McGowan Mandatory Training - Mandatory Training Group UK -" data-pf-type="Image3" class="sc-igXgud kyVXGU pf-25_"/><p class="sc-gfqkcP gZrsGP pf-26_" data-pf-type="Paragraph"><span data-pf-type="Text" class="sc-jdhwqr jnAcXR pf-28_">The journey toward mandatory training began with discussions in the UK Parliament, where Members of Parliament passionately argued for the urgent need to improve health outcomes for individuals with learning disabilities and autism. These discussions shed light on the alarming statistics and heartbreaking stories, emphasising the critical need for health and social care professionals to receive comprehensive training to provide adequate support.
</span></p><h3 data-pf-type="Heading" class="sc-bBHHxi aumKe pf-29_ _Y6RW61"><span data-pf-type="Text" class="sc-jdhwqr jnAcXR pf-31_">The Oliver McGowan case: A catalyst for change


</span></h3><img src="https://cdn.shopify.com/s/files/1/0937/2788/files/The_Oliver_McGowan_case_A_catalyst_for_change_-_Oliver_McGowan_Mandatory_Training_-_Mandatory_Training_Group_UK.png?v=1686151848" srcSet="https://cdn.shopify.com/s/files/1/0937/2788/files/The_Oliver_McGowan_case_A_catalyst_for_change_-_Oliver_McGowan_Mandatory_Training_-_Mandatory_Training_Group_UK.png?v=1686151848 1536w, https://cdn.shopify.com/s/files/1/0937/2788/files/The_Oliver_McGowan_case_A_catalyst_for_change_-_Oliver_McGowan_Mandatory_Training_-_Mandatory_Training_Group_UK_500x.png?v=1686151848 320w" width="1306" height="1934" alt="The Oliver McGowan case: A catalyst for change - Oliver McGowan Mandatory Training - Mandatory Training Group UK -" title="The Oliver McGowan case: A catalyst for change - Oliver McGowan Mandatory Training - Mandatory Training Group UK -" data-pf-type="Image3" class="sc-igXgud kyVXGU pf-32_"/><p class="sc-gfqkcP gZrsGP pf-33_" data-pf-type="Paragraph"><span data-pf-type="Text" class="sc-jdhwqr jnAcXR pf-35_">At the heart of these discussions was the tragic case of Oliver McGowan, a young man who lost his life due to improper medication. Oliver's parents, Tom and Paula McGowan, emerged as tireless campaigners, working tirelessly to ensure that no other family would endure a similar tragedy. Their determination, along with the support of other advocates and allies, galvanised the push for mandatory training, recognising the urgent need to equip health and social care professionals with the necessary knowledge and skills.
<br> 
</span></p><h3 data-pf-type="Heading" class="sc-bBHHxi aumKe pf-36_ _Y6RW61"><span data-pf-type="Text" class="sc-jdhwqr jnAcXR pf-38_">A collaborative effort: Trials and evaluation






</span></h3><img src="https://cdn.shopify.com/s/files/1/0937/2788/files/A_collaborative_effort_Trials_and_evaluation_-_Oliver_McGowan_Mandatory_Training_-_Mandatory_Training_Group_UK.png?v=1686151942" srcSet="https://cdn.shopify.com/s/files/1/0937/2788/files/A_collaborative_effort_Trials_and_evaluation_-_Oliver_McGowan_Mandatory_Training_-_Mandatory_Training_Group_UK.png?v=1686151942 1536w, https://cdn.shopify.com/s/files/1/0937/2788/files/A_collaborative_effort_Trials_and_evaluation_-_Oliver_McGowan_Mandatory_Training_-_Mandatory_Training_Group_UK_500x.png?v=1686151942 320w" width="1761" height="1174" alt="A collaborative effort: Trials and evaluation - Oliver McGowan Mandatory Training - Mandatory Training Group UK -" title="A collaborative effort: Trials and evaluation - Oliver McGowan Mandatory Training - Mandatory Training Group UK -" data-pf-type="Image3" class="sc-igXgud kyVXGU pf-39_"/><p class="sc-gfqkcP gZrsGP pf-40_" data-pf-type="Paragraph"><span data-pf-type="Text" class="sc-jdhwqr jnAcXR pf-42_">Recognising the significance of the cause, national partners, including Gloucestershire Healthcare, joined forces to develop and implement a standardised training package. A national trial was conducted to assess the effectiveness and feasibility of the training programme. Through collaborative efforts, professionals from diverse disciplines contributed their expertise to shape the training program.

<br>
</span></p><h3 data-pf-type="Heading" class="sc-bBHHxi aumKe pf-43_ _Y6RW61"><span data-pf-type="Text" class="sc-jdhwqr jnAcXR pf-45_">Parliamentary directives: Enforcing change


</span></h3><img src="https://cdn.shopify.com/s/files/1/0937/2788/files/Parliamentary_directives_Enforcing_change_-_Oliver_McGowan_Mandatory_Training_-_Mandatory_Training_Group_UK.png?v=1686152188" srcSet="https://cdn.shopify.com/s/files/1/0937/2788/files/Parliamentary_directives_Enforcing_change_-_Oliver_McGowan_Mandatory_Training_-_Mandatory_Training_Group_UK.png?v=1686152188 1536w, https://cdn.shopify.com/s/files/1/0937/2788/files/Parliamentary_directives_Enforcing_change_-_Oliver_McGowan_Mandatory_Training_-_Mandatory_Training_Group_UK_500x.png?v=1686152188 320w" width="1810" height="1123" alt="Parliamentary directives: Enforcing change - Oliver McGowan Mandatory Training - Mandatory Training Group UK -" title="Parliamentary directives: Enforcing change - Oliver McGowan Mandatory Training - Mandatory Training Group UK -" data-pf-type="Image3" class="sc-igXgud kyVXGU pf-46_"/><p class="sc-gfqkcP gZrsGP pf-47_" data-pf-type="Paragraph"><span data-pf-type="Text" class="sc-jdhwqr jnAcXR pf-49_">Following the trials and evaluations, the Parliament recognised the imperative to enforce change and improve care for individuals with learning disabilities and autism. The Health and Care Act 2022 was passed, solidifying the learning disability and autism awareness training as a legal requirement for all health and social care workers. This directive ensures that professionals receive the necessary training to provide better health outcomes and compassionate care.
